    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained by its previous owner. Mechanically, it performs reliably with a smooth engine and transmission, supported by a documented service history. The interior is well-preserved and clean, showing only light wear consistent with its age, while the exterior remains in great shape with only a few minor surface blemishes. A solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned car.",
